{"primaryContentSections":[{"kind":"declarations","declarations":[{"tokens":[{"kind":"keyword","text":"var"},{"kind":"text","text":" "},{"kind":"identifier","text":"delegate"},{"kind":"text","text":": "},{"kind":"typeIdentifier","identifier":"doc:\/\/com.vuzix.UltraliteSDK\/documentation\/UltraliteSDK\/AutoScrollerDelegate","preciseIdentifier":"s:12UltraliteSDK20AutoScrollerDelegateP","text":"AutoScrollerDelegate"},{"kind":"text","text":"?"}],"languages":["swift"],"platforms":["iOS"]}]}],"schemaVersion":{"major":0,"minor":3,"patch":0},"sections":[],"variants":[{"paths":["\/documentation\/ultralitesdk\/scrolllayout\/autoscroller\/delegate"],"traits":[{"interfaceLanguage":"swift"}]}],"identifier":{"url":"doc:\/\/com.vuzix.UltraliteSDK\/documentation\/UltraliteSDK\/ScrollLayout\/AutoScroller\/delegate","interfaceLanguage":"swift"},"abstract":[{"type":"text","text":"Delegate for listenting for the scrolled event"}],"kind":"symbol","metadata":{"fragments":[{"kind":"keyword","text":"var"},{"kind":"text","text":" "},{"kind":"identifier","text":"delegate"},{"kind":"text","text":": "},{"kind":"typeIdentifier","text":"AutoScrollerDelegate","preciseIdentifier":"s:12UltraliteSDK20AutoScrollerDelegateP"},{"kind":"text","text":"?"}],"title":"delegate","roleHeading":"Instance Property","role":"symbol","symbolKind":"property","externalID":"s:12UltraliteSDK12ScrollLayoutC12AutoScrollerC8delegateAA0eF8Delegate_pSgvp","modules":[{"name":"UltraliteSDK"}]},"hierarchy":{"paths":[["doc:\/\/com.vuzix.UltraliteSDK\/documentation\/UltraliteSDK","doc:\/\/com.vuzix.UltraliteSDK\/documentation\/UltraliteSDK\/ScrollLayout","doc:\/\/com.vuzix.UltraliteSDK\/documentation\/UltraliteSDK\/ScrollLayout\/AutoScroller"]]},"references":{"doc://com.vuzix.UltraliteSDK/documentation/UltraliteSDK":{"role":"collection","title":"UltraliteSDK","abstract":[{"type":"text","text":"Use this SDK to easily send text and images to your Vuxix smart glasses."}],"identifier":"doc:\/\/com.vuzix.UltraliteSDK\/documentation\/UltraliteSDK","kind":"symbol","type":"topic","url":"\/documentation\/ultralitesdk"},"doc://com.vuzix.UltraliteSDK/documentation/UltraliteSDK/ScrollLayout/AutoScroller":{"role":"symbol","title":"ScrollLayout.AutoScroller","fragments":[{"kind":"keyword","text":"class"},{"kind":"text","text":" "},{"kind":"identifier","text":"AutoScroller"}],"abstract":[{"type":"text","text":"AutoScroller is a utility class to send a large known block of predfined text to the glasses to be smoothly scrolled."},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"This is simlar to what is seen on a teleprompter or in movie credits."},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"This class was written using the "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"ScrollLayout"},{"type":"text","text":" commands and is nothing more than a convience class."},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"Everything used this class can be written from the public SDK."},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"It scrolls the text much like a teleprompter would with basic commands to pause and resume the scrolling."},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"The duration (speed) of the scrolling can be modified while scrolling by seting the "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"duration"},{"type":"text","text":" property."},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"It can support any language that the font supports."},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"If the content is not known up front, or subject to change, this is the utility class will not work (use "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"LiveText"},{"type":"text","text":" instance instead)."}],"identifier":"doc:\/\/com.vuzix.UltraliteSDK\/documentation\/UltraliteSDK\/ScrollLayout\/AutoScroller","kind":"symbol","type":"topic","navigatorTitle":[{"kind":"identifier","text":"AutoScroller"}],"url":"\/documentation\/ultralitesdk\/scrolllayout\/autoscroller"},"doc://com.vuzix.UltraliteSDK/documentation/UltraliteSDK/ScrollLayout/AutoScroller/delegate":{"role":"symbol","title":"delegate","fragments":[{"kind":"keyword","text":"var"},{"kind":"text","text":" "},{"kind":"identifier","text":"delegate"},{"kind":"text","text":": "},{"kind":"typeIdentifier","text":"AutoScrollerDelegate","preciseIdentifier":"s:12UltraliteSDK20AutoScrollerDelegateP"},{"kind":"text","text":"?"}],"abstract":[{"type":"text","text":"Delegate for listenting for the scrolled event"}],"identifier":"doc:\/\/com.vuzix.UltraliteSDK\/documentation\/UltraliteSDK\/ScrollLayout\/AutoScroller\/delegate","kind":"symbol","type":"topic","url":"\/documentation\/ultralitesdk\/scrolllayout\/autoscroller\/delegate"},"doc://com.vuzix.UltraliteSDK/documentation/UltraliteSDK/ScrollLayout":{"role":"symbol","title":"ScrollLayout","fragments":[{"kind":"keyword","text":"class"},{"kind":"text","text":" "},{"kind":"identifier","text":"ScrollLayout"}],"abstract":[{"type":"text","text":"When Ultralite.requestControl with a .scroll layout type .. this is the class you interate with to draw scrolling text to the screen."},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"Once the layout is .scrolled you must send one configure message to tell the layout how to setup.  It will setup the slice height and how many slices are visible."},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"There are two supported modes: autoScroll on\/off"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"When autoScroll is true, the slices are automatically scrolled.  Subscribe to the delgate and listen for the scrolled callback, when you get it send another slice of text"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"When autoScroll is false, you can drive the slices and how they look on the screen.  You can send all the slices at once or send one at a time and animate it onto the screen at the current time."}],"identifier":"doc:\/\/com.vuzix.UltraliteSDK\/documentation\/UltraliteSDK\/ScrollLayout","kind":"symbol","type":"topic","navigatorTitle":[{"kind":"identifier","text":"ScrollLayout"}],"url":"\/documentation\/ultralitesdk\/scrolllayout"},"doc://com.vuzix.UltraliteSDK/documentation/UltraliteSDK/AutoScrollerDelegate":{"role":"symbol","title":"AutoScrollerDelegate","fragments":[{"kind":"keyword","text":"protocol"},{"kind":"text","text":" "},{"kind":"identifier","text":"AutoScrollerDelegate"}],"abstract":[{"type":"text","text":"AutoScroll class Delegate"}],"identifier":"doc:\/\/com.vuzix.UltraliteSDK\/documentation\/UltraliteSDK\/AutoScrollerDelegate","kind":"symbol","type":"topic","navigatorTitle":[{"kind":"identifier","text":"AutoScrollerDelegate"}],"url":"\/documentation\/ultralitesdk\/autoscrollerdelegate"}}}